SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT COUNT (TPCH_ID), CAST(SUM (TPCH_AMOUNTCURRCHEQUE/(case when A.CURA_OPPOSITE_RATES= 'Y' then 1/A.CURA_EXCHGRATE_FL else A.CURA_EXCHGRATE_FL end) * (case when B.CURA_OPPOSITE_RATES='Y' then 1/B.CURA_EXCHGRATE_FL else B.CURA_EXCHGRATE_FL end)) AS DECIMAL (14,2)), TPCH_BANK_ADMNO, TPCH_BANK_LEDG_NO, min(ADMN_CURRENCY) FROM :1, :2 , :3 , :4 WHERE ADMN_NO = TPCH_ADMNO and A.CURA_CODE=TPCH_CURRENCY and A.CURA_ADMNO = ADMN_ADMNO_RATES AND B.CURA_CODE= ADMN_CURRENCY and B.CURA_ADMNO = ADMN_ADMNO_RATES :5 GROUP BY TPCH_BANK_ADMNO, TPCH_BANK_LEDG_NO, ADMN_CURRENCY
